        "id": 1114299
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-11-03T02:05:12Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "why do we need any sinkStats{} for the purpose of just logging how long did it take to shutdown the server?\n\n\tstart :\u003d clock.Now(ctx)\n\tdefer func() {\n\t\tlogging.Debugf(ctx, \"Shutdown took %s\", clock.Since(ctx, start), err)\n\t}()\n\n?",
      "parentUuid": "8aeb6504_57780d8c",
      "revId": "9b99e6253aa43d628a4291ce1ef0155272ede7af",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba"
    },
